http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/httpd/httpd/branches/2.2.x/modules/filters/mod_filter.c?view=markup#l577

rxend = ap_strchr_c(match, '/');

should be:

rxend = ap_strrchr_c(match, '/');

Because a regex of /application//xml/ will match anything beginning with "application", ie, application/zip as it is picking up the first slash as the regex end.
